# EventCatalog site content lives here.
#
# This directory is bind-mounted read-only into the `eventcatalog` container at
# `/app/site`. If this file did not exist, Docker would auto-create the
# directory as root:root on first `docker compose up`, which then blocks
# Holyfields generation from populating it from the host.
#
# Populated by Holyfields generation output (see
# ../../../docs/architecture/v3-holyfields-contract-work.md). Until HOLYF-2
# lands, EventCatalog serves an empty UI.
